palindorme.js - this program asks user to enter a word, using while loop the program determines whether or not the word is a palindrome 
(whether it reads the same forwards and backwards eg  "racecar")

while.js - the program asks user to enter a number until user enters -1. Then the program stops and calculates average of all numbers entered
excluding the -1

quiz.js - if user chooses wrong answer they are asked to answer again. The program ends when the user guesses correctly or they don't wish to 
answer anymore
